First, delete all cells in the notebook to start fresh. Then: AnnData (mouse brain). Expression-only. **Hierarchical, clustering-first**:
1) Normalize/log1p; HVGs(3000); PCA(50); neighbors(30); Leiden(0.6).
2) rank_genes_groups('wilcoxon').
3) Level-1: Non-neuronal partitioning.
4) Level-2 (within Non-neuronal): identify and merge clusters you consider Astrocyte from your ranked markers (do not hardcode).
5) Re-rank Astrocyte vs all non-Astrocyte cells to infer the **agent’s Astrocyte marker set**. Output top-13 markers (uppercase).

                    IMPORTANT: When you have completed this task, include the text "[EVAL_COMPLETE]" at the end of your summary in submit_response.
